  * Session.testFile(): general solution for an asyncron file generation.
  * Session.forceReload(): general solution for page reloading.
  * Fix: Deletes user data only if it exists.
  * Fix: Preloading can have 2 or 3 arguments.
  * Message when we wait for the partition info.
